text: KZDV (99.5 FM) is a radio station licensed to Rattan, Oklahoma, United States. The station is currently owned by Will Payne ==History== This station was assigned call sign KZDV on November 19, 2012. ==References== ==External links== *http://www.k955.com/kzdv/ ZDV Category:Contemporary Christian radio stations in the United States Category:Radio stations established in 2012 ZDV
